
 
Some process gains include synergic problem solving because all group members may build off each others ideas on how to manage lockdown. Another pro is that there is a specialization of roles such as transportation secretary and agriculture secretary which can contribute with their expertise to make the optimal decision.
Some group losses may include groupthink and also conflict if there is a lack of identification because the proposed solution doesn’t align with the goals of some team members.
They were at risk of groupthink as they all belonged to the same government there may have been pressure to reach common ground and agree on an initiative. Thus even if some group members didn’t agree, they would not have said it outloud but would go with the majority of the group anyway.
